"main0108.xhp\n"
"par_id443534340\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".uno:SendFeedback\">Opens a feedback form in the web browser, where users can report software bugs.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".uno:SendFeedback\">ເປີດແບບຟອມຄຳຄິດເຫັນໃນເວັບບຣາວເຊີ, ບ່ອນທີ່ຜູ້ໃຊ້ສາມາດລາຍງານຂໍ້ຜິດພາດຂອງຊອບແວໄດ້.</ahelp>"

