#. Cwsus
#: main0650.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0650.xhp\n"
"hd_id3153089\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<link href=\"text/shared/main0650.xhp\">Java Platform Support</link>"
msgstr "<link href=\"text/shared/main0650.xhp\">ການສະໜັບສະໜູນແພລັດຟອມ Java</link>"

#. dPzDx
#: main0650.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0650.xhp\n"
"par_id3152363\n"
"help.text"
msgid "$[officename] supports the Java platform for running applications and components based on the JavaBeans architecture."
msgstr "$[officename] ສະໜັບສະໜູນແພລັດຟອມ Java ສຳລັບການລັນແອັບພລິເຄຊັນ ແລະ ອົງປະກອບຕ່າງໆ ໂດຍອີງໃສ່ສະຖາປັດຕະຍະກຳ JavaBeans."

#. Bwg5V
#: main0650.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0650.xhp\n"
"par_id3154751\n"
"help.text"
msgid "For $[officename] to support the Java platform, you must install the Java 2 Runtime Environment software. When you installed $[officename], you automatically received the option to install these files if they were not yet installed. You can also install these files now if required."
msgstr "ເພື່ອໃຫ້ $[officename] ສາມາດສະໜັບສະໜູນແພລັດຟອມ Java ໄດ້, ທ່ານຕ້ອງຕິດຕັ້ງຊອບແວ Java 2 Runtime Environment. ເມື່ອທ່ານຕິດຕັ້ງ $[officename], ທ່ານຈະໄດ້ຮັບຕົວເລືອກໃຫ້ຕິດຕັ້ງໄຟລ໌ເຫຼົ່ານີ້ໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ ຫາກພວກມັນຍັງບໍ່ທັນໄດ້ຕິດຕັ້ງ. ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດຕິດຕັ້ງໄຟລ໌ເຫຼົ່ານີ້ໄດ້ໃນຕອນນີ້ຫາກຕ້ອງການ."

#. wFYWg
#: main0650.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0650.xhp\n"
"par_id3155338\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The Java platform support needs to be activated under $[officename] to run Java applications."
msgstr "ການສະໜັບສະໜູນແພລັດຟອມ Java ຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງໄດ້ຮັບການເປີດໃຊ້ພາຍໃຕ້ $[officename] ເພື່ອລັນແອັບພລິເຄຊັນ Java."

#. H2Vk4
#: main0650.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0650.xhp\n"
"par_id3155892\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Enable Java platform support by choosing <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>%PRODUCTNAME - Preferences</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>Tools - Options</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> - </emph><link href=\"text/shared/optionen/java.xhp\"><emph>$[officename] - Advanced</emph></link>."
msgstr "ເປີດໃຊ້ການສະໜັບສະໜູນແພລັດຟອມ Java ໂດຍການເລືອກ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>%PRODUCTNAME - ການຕັ້ງຄ່າ</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>ເຄື່ອງມື - ຕົວເລືອກ</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> - </emph><link href=\"text/shared/optionen/java.xhp\"><emph>$[officename] - ຂັ້ນສູງ</emph></link>."

#. NcDL4
#: main0650.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0650.xhp\n"
"par_id9116183\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Before you can use a JDBC driver, you need to add its class path. Choose <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">%PRODUCTNAME - Preferences</caseinline><defaultinline>Tools - Options</defaultinline></switchinline> - %PRODUCTNAME - Advanced, and click the Class Path button. After you add the path information, restart %PRODUCTNAME."
msgstr "ກ່ອນທີ່ທ່ານຈະສາມາດໃຊ້ໄດຣເວີ JDBC ໄດ້, ທ່ານຕ້ອງເພີ່ມ class path ຂອງມັນກ່ອນ. ເລືອກ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">%PRODUCTNAME - ການຕັ້ງຄ່າ</caseinline><defaultinline>ເຄື່ອງມື - ຕົວເລືອກ</defaultinline></switchinline> - %PRODUCTNAME - ຂັ້ນສູງ, ແລະ ຄລິກປຸ່ມ Class Path. ຫຼັງຈາກທີ່ທ່ານເພີ່ມຂໍ້ມູນເສັ້ນທາງແລ້ວ, ໃຫ້ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ %PRODUCTNAME ໃໝ່."

#. 9YUwB
#: main0650.xhp
msgctxt ""
"main0650.xhp\n"
"par_id3153822\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Your modifications at the <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>%PRODUCTNAME - Preferences</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>Tools - Options</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> - $[officename] - Advanced</emph> tab page will be used even if the Java Virtual Machine (JVM) has been started already. After any modifications to the ClassPath you must restart $[officename]. The same is true for modifications under <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>%PRODUCTNAME - Preferences</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>Tools - Options</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> - Internet - Proxy</emph>. Only the boxes \"HTTP Proxy\" and their ports do not require a restart—they will be evaluated when you click <emph>OK</emph>."
msgstr "ການປັບປ່ຽນຂອງທ່ານໃນໜ້າແທັບ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>%PRODUCTNAME - ການຕັ້ງຄ່າ</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>ເຄື່ອງມື - ຕົວເລືອກ</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> - $[officename] - ຂັ້ນສູງ</emph> ຈະຖືກນຳໃຊ້ ເຖິງແມ່ນວ່າ Java Virtual Machine (JVM) ຈະຖືກເລີ່ມຕົ້ນໄປແລ້ວກໍຕາມ. ຫຼັງຈາກການປັບປ່ຽນ ClassPath ໃດໆ ທ່ານຕ້ອງເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ $[officename] ໃໝ່. ເຊັ່ນດຽວກັນກັບການປັບປ່ຽນພາຍໃຕ້ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>%PRODUCTNAME - ການຕັ້ງຄ່າ</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>ເຄື່ອງມື - ຕົວເລືອກ</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> - ອິນເຕີເນັດ - Proxy</emph>. ສະເພາະຊ່ອງ \"HTTP Proxy\" ແລະ ພອດຂອງພວກມັນເທົ່ານັ້ນທີ່ບໍ່ຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງເລີ່ມຕົ້ນໃໝ່—ພວກມັນຈະມີຜົນທັນທີເມື່ອທ່ານຄລິກ <emph>ຕົກລົງ</emph>."

